om de orde te herstellen in een gebied dat wordt gedomineerd door wetteloosheid en onrecht."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Django je odhodlán vykonat spravedlnost a čelí nebezpečným výzvám a krvavým střetům, aby obnovil pořádek na území ovládaném bezprávím a nespravedlností."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Django imbatible","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Decidido a exigir justicia, Django se enfrenta a peligrosos desafíos y sangrientos enfrentamientos para restaurar el orden en un territorio dominado por la anarquía y la injusticia."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Django imbatible","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Decidido a hacer justicia por su cuenta, Django se adentra en un territorio despiadado donde reinan la violencia y la anarquía. Entre duelos y desafíos letales, tendrá que arriesgarlo todo para devolver el orden allí donde ahora sólo parece dominar el caos."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"无可争议的姜戈","runtime":84,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"在这片法外之地，不公与暴行肆虐横行。姜戈以血为誓，披荆斩棘，在枪火与刀锋的洗礼中，为扭曲的大地重铸正义的法则。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"უძლეველი ჯანგო","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"ジャンゴ無差別級","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":1011477,"adult":false,"title":"Karate Kid: Legends","video":false,"overview":"After a family tragedy, kung fu prodigy Li Fong is uprooted from his home in Beijing and forced to move to New York City with his mother. When a new friend needs his help, Li enters a karate competition – but his skills alone aren't enough. Li's kung fu teacher Mr. Han enlists original Karate Kid Daniel LaRusso for help, and Li learns a new way to fight, merging their two styles into one for the ultimate martial arts showdown.","genre_ids":[28,12,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":11.6199,"vote_count":1112,"poster_path":"/c90Lt7OQGsOmhv6x4JoFdoHzw5l.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-08","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/7Q2CmqIVJuDAESPPp76rWIiA0AD.jpg","original_title":"Karate Kid: Legends","original_language":"en"},{"id":9086,"adult":false,"title":"Young Guns II","video":false,"overview":"Three of the original five \"young guns\" — Billy the Kid, Jose Chavez y Chavez, and Doc Scurlock — return in Young Guns, Part 2, which is the story of Billy the Kid and his race to safety in Old Mexico while being trailed by a group of government agents led by Pat Garrett.","genre_ids":[37,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5669,"vote_count":579,"poster_path":"/7kMjla98srGHlFzAEmoGRcr6GN1.jpg","release_date":"1990-08-01","vote_average":6.503,"backdrop_path":"/sQNPWOTzl5kkZTW5ogSu0uSnreB.jpg","original_title":"Young Guns II","original_language":"en"},{"id":157336,"adult":false,"title":"Interstellar","video":false,"overview":"The adventures of a group of explorers who make use of a newly discovered wormhole to surpass the limitations on human space travel and conquer the vast distances involved in an interstellar voyage.","genre_ids":[12,18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":43.1132,"vote_count":38961,"poster_path":"/gEU2QniE6E77NI6lCU6MxlNBvIx.jpg","release_date":"2014-11-05","vote_average":8.467,"backdrop_path":"/2ssWTSVklAEc98frZUQhgtGHx7s.jpg","original_title":"Interstellar","original_language":"en"},{"id":597,"adult":false,"title":"Titanic","video":false,"overview":"101-year-old Rose DeWitt Bukater tells the story of her life aboard the Titanic, 84 years later. A young Rose boards the ship with her mother and fiancé. Meanwhile, Jack Dawson and Fabrizio De Rossi win third-class tickets aboard the ship. Rose tells the whole story from Titanic's departure through to its death—on its first and last voyage—on April 15, 1912.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":28.4976,"vote_count":26827,"poster_path":"/9xjZS2rlVxm8SFx8kPC3aIGCOYQ.jpg","release_date":"1997-12-18","vote_average":7.903,"backdrop_path":"/xnHVX37XZEp33hhCbYlQFq7ux1J.jpg","original_title":"Titanic","original_language":"en"},{"id":475557,"adult":false,"title":"Joker","video":false,"overview":"During the 1980s, a failed stand-up comedian is driven insane and turns to a life of crime and chaos in Gotham City while becoming an infamous psychopathic crime figure.","genre_ids":[80,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.0422,"vote_count":27338,"poster_path":"/udDclJoHjfjb8Ekgsd4FDteOkCU.jpg","release_date":"2019-10-01","vote_average":8.128,"backdrop_path":"/hO7KbdvGOtDdeg0W4Y5nKEHeDDh.jpg","original_title":"Joker","original_language":"en"},{"id":11324,"adult":false,"title":"Shutter Island","video":false,"overview":"World War II soldier-turned-U.S. Marshal Teddy Daniels investigates the disappearance of a patient from a hospital for the criminally insane, but his efforts are compromised by troubling visions and a mysterious doctor.","genre_ids":[18,53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.6244,"vote_count":25460,"poster_path":"/nrmXQ0zcZUL8jFLrakWc90IR8z9.jpg","release_date":"2010-02-14","vote_average":8.2,"backdrop_path":"/8xt8AMb1OKC63AdhNSaYBWxB4Iq.jpg","original_title":"Shutter Island","original_language":"en"},{"id":466272,"adult":false,"title":"Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood","video":false,"overview":"Los Angeles, 1969. TV star Rick Dalton, a struggling actor specializing in westerns, and stuntman Cliff Booth, his best friend, try to survive in a constantly changing movie industry. Dalton is the neighbor of the young and promising actress and model Sharon Tate, who has just married the prestigious Polish director Roman Polanski…","genre_ids":[35,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.721,"vote_count":14579,"poster_path":"/8j58iEBw9pOXFD2L0nt0ZXeHviB.jpg","release_date":"2019-07-24","vote_average":7.423,"backdrop_path":"/kKTPv9LKKs5L3oO1y5FNObxAPWI.jpg","original_title":"Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood","original_language":"en"},{"id":37165,"adult":false,"title":"The Truman Show","video":false,"overview":"An insurance salesman begins to suspect that his whole life is actually some sort of reality TV show.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":16.282,"vote_count":19832,"poster_path":"/vuza0WqY239yBXOadKlGwJsZJFE.jpg","release_date":"1998-06-04","vote_average":8.151,"backdrop_path":"/aCHn2TXYJfzPXQKA6r9mKPbMlUB.jpg","original_title":"The Truman Show","original_language":"en"},{"id":105,"adult":false,"title":"Back to the Future","video":false,"overview":"Eighties teenager Marty McFly is accidentally sent back in time to 1955, inadvertently disrupting his parents' first meeting and attracting his mother's romantic interest. Marty must repair the damage to history by rekindling his parents' romance and - with the help of his eccentric inventor friend Doc Brown - return to 1985.","genre_ids":[12,35,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.5525,"vote_count":21421,"poster_path":"/vN5B5WgYscRGcQpVhHl6p9DDTP0.jpg","release_date":"1985-07-03","vote_average":8.324,"backdrop_path":"/qskzmLTbarKnXDbo2HRj4NJ3vcW.jpg","original_title":"Back to the Future","original_language":"en"},{"id":872585,"adult":false,"title":"Oppenheimer","video":false,"overview":"The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":19.7563,"vote_count":11389,"