 day ends, they question whether school will ever be the same.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.7903,"vote_count":8415,"poster_path":"/gp4zlj7wgbiofLMNsTPndMuO3PN.jpg","release_date":"1985-02-15","vote_average":7.725,"backdrop_path":"/kjVgUMsG0PKBXzlP8HGNQpWDxAX.jpg","original_title":"The Breakfast Club","original_language":"en"},{"id":14,"adult":false,"title":"American Beauty","video":false,"overview":"Lester Burnham, a depressed suburban father in a mid-life crisis, decides to turn his hectic life around after developing an infatuation with his daughter's attractive friend.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.4774,"vote_count":12827,"poster_path":"/wby9315QzVKdW9BonAefg8jGTTb.jpg","release_date":"1999-09-15","vote_average":8.002,"backdrop_path":"/2ndw55F40IkALzWyjCCza3M6nqM.jpg","original_title":"American Beauty","original_language":"en"},{"id":10681,"adult":false,"title":"WALL·E","video":false,"overview":"After hundreds of years doing what he was built for, WALL•E— a robot designed to clean up the earth—discovers a new purpose in life when he meets a sleek search robot named EVE. EVE comes to realize that WALL•E has inadvertently stumbled upon the key to the planet's future, and races back to space to report to the humans. Meanwhile, WALL•E chases EVE across the galaxy and sets into motion one of the most imaginative adventures ever brought to the big screen.","genre_ids":[16,10751,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.1365,"vote_count":19948,"poster_path":"/hbhFnRzzg6ZDmm8YAmxBnQpQIPh.jpg","release_date":"2008-06-22","vote_average":8.107,"backdrop_path":"/fK5ssgvtI43z19FoWigdlqgpLRE.jpg","original_title":"WALL·E","original_language":"en"},{"id":577922,"adult":false,"title":"Tenet","video":false,"overview":"Armed with only one word - Tenet - and fighting for the survival of the entire world, the Protagonist journeys through a twilight world of international espionage on a mission that will unfold in something beyond 